title: Ep.181 Japan's Recent Run Will Be Short-Lived
itunes:title: Japan's Recent Run Will Be Short-Lived
description: Keith Fitz-Gerald, chief investment strategist for Money Map Press and 20-year veteran of the markets, says Japan is not the U.S., or won't be able to inflate its way out of its massive debts. Keith also explains the exact cause for the 15% two-day drop in gold prices - and shares his favorite stocks to buy today.
